            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# SuperScreenshot 0.9.80

- 支持截取其他应用和本应用已展开的菜单。
- 快捷键按下时冻结多屏幕画面，避免菜单在框选前收起。
- 统一冻结画面的框选、取色和截图结果。

---

- Added capture support for open menus in any app.
- Freezes all displays when the shortcut is pressed so menus remain visible.
- Uses the same frozen frame for selection, color sampling, and output.
]]></description>
